<div class="com-share" data-id="15798" data-title="《Facebook 发现点赞可不够》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15798/medium/15798.jpg?1444347632" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15798.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
